hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: A book of First Class stamps levonorgestrel custo To me, the product represents just the sort of earnest, middle-class hypocrisy that sees families obsess over the enzyme levels in their compost bin, yet own two cars and whizz off to Florida a the drop of a hat for some winter sun. It’s the ultimate token gesture, the sanitary equivalent of being voraciously anti-smoking, but doing cocaine at the weekends - ‘if someone else has got it in, I’d never buy my own’ kind of thing.
